# Docs last updated for version

v1.10.1

## How to use this file

When updating docs next time, run:

```bash
# Get all changes since docs were last updated
git log v1.10.1..HEAD --oneline
```

Then update this file to the new version after the docs PR is merged.

## What was covered in this update

- `orun run` positional argument `[component|planhash]` (added v1.9.0, v1.10.0)
- `orun plan` positional argument `[component]` (added v1.10.0)
- `orun run` new flags: `--component-concurrency`, `--background`, `--isolation`, `--keep-workspaces`
- `orun run` change detection flags: `--changed`, `--base`, `--head`, `--files`, `--uncommitted`, `--untracked`, `--explain`
- `orun plan` / `orun component` `--explain` flag
- CI auto-detection for `--changed` (added v1.7.0)
- `--plan` flag marked deprecated in favor of positional argument
